      "text": "The Bielskis always went to Platon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was the head, from the whole the partisans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were complaining that the Russian and the partisans, they hated Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
